# VPN_SWITCH_DNS_wireguard - WireGuard DNS server
#
# Default DNS server for WireGuard connections.
# This follows the VPN_SWITCH_DNS_<protocol> naming convention for
# protocol-agnostic DNS server lookup.
#
# Default: 10.2.0.1 (VPN provider WireGuard gateway)
#
# VPN provider's WireGuard service assigns IPs from 10.2.0.0/8 with gateway at 10.2.0.1
# This DNS server is used when the WireGuard config doesn't specify DNS explicitly.
#
# Behavior:
#   - Used as fallback if config doesn't contain DNS directives
#   - Can be overridden per-database via setenv command
#   - Configured via resolvconf and requires local_unbound reload
